dc_title_s: The Daily Telegraph war map no. 24 of the British front
dc_description_s: Shows fighting lines before the July 1st, 1916 advance and approximate fighting line on July 1st, 1917.; Covers the region between Lille and St. Quentin in northern France and West Flanders, Belgium.; Includes 4 inset maps.|99 x 57 centimeters|Scale approximately 1:190,000|General Map Collection
